<document xmlns="http://cnx.rice.edu/cnxml" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
<title>Hlutfallslegur styrkur sýra og basa</title>
<metadata xmlns:md="http://cnx.rice.edu/mdml">
  <md:content-id>m68805</md:content-id>
  <md:title>Hlutfallslegur styrkur sýra og basa</md:title>
  <md:abstract><para id="para-00001">Í lok þessa kafla muntu geta:</para><list id="list-00001"><item>Metið hlutfallslegan styrk sýra og basa út frá jónunarfastanum þeirra</item><item>Rökstutt þróun í styrk sýra og basa í tengslum við sameindabyggingu</item><item>Framkvæmt jafnvægisútreikninga fyrir kerfi með veikum sýrum og bösum</item></list></md:abstract>
  <md:uuid>5405aa2f-8793-467b-ae1d-1795f1142207</md:uuid>
</metadata>

<content>
<section id="fs-idm477446592">
<title>Jónunarfastar sýra og basa</title>
<para id="fs-idm193375984">Hlutfallslegur styrkur sýru eða basa er hversu mikið efnið jónast þegar það er leyst upp í vatni. Ef jónunarhvarfið er nánast fullkomið er sýran eða basinn kallaður <emphasis effect="italics">sterkur</emphasis>; ef tiltölulega lítil jónun á sér stað er sýran eða basinn veikur. Eins og augljóst verður í þessum kafla eru miklu fleiri veikar sýrur og basar en sterkir. Algengustu sterku sýrurnar og basarnir eru taldir upp í <link target-id="CNX_Chem_14_03_strong"/>.</para>
<figure id="CNX_Chem_14_03_strong" class="scaled-down">
<media id="fs-idp3283088" alt="This table has seven rows and two columns. The first row is a header row, and it labels each column, “6 Strong Acids,” and, “6 Strong Bases.” Under the “6 Strong Acids” column are the following: H C l O subscript 4 perchloric acid; H C l hydrochloric acid; H B r hydrobromic acid; H I hydroiodic acid; H N O subscript 3 nitric acid; H subscript 2 S O subscript 4 sulfuric acid. Under the “6 Strong Bases” column are the following: L i O H lithium hydroxide; N a O H sodium hydroxide; K O H potassium hydroxide; C a ( O H ) subscript 2 calcium hydroxide; S r ( O H ) subscript 2 strontium hydroxide; B a ( O H ) subscript 2 barium hydroxide.">
<image mime-type="image/jpeg" src="../../media/CNX_Chem_14_03_strong.jpg"/>
</media>
<caption>Nokkrar af algengum sterkum sýrum og bösum eru taldar upp hér.</caption>
</figure>
<para id="fs-idp107824512">Hægt er að magngreina hlutfallslegan styrk sýra með því að mæla jafnvægisfasta þeirra í vatnslausnum. Í lausnum með sama styrk jónast sterkari sýrur í meira mæli og gefa því hærri styrk hýdróníumjóna en veikari sýrur. Jafnvægisfastinn fyrir sýru er kallaður <term id="term-00001">sýrujónunarfasti, <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>a</sub> (e. acid-ionization constant, ka)</term>. Fyrir efnahvarf sýru HA:</para>
<equation id="fs-idm122858592" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>HA</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>l</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:msup><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mtext>A</m:mtext><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>,</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idp44134944">er sýrujónunarfastinn skrifaður</para>
<equation id="fs-idp97870288" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>a</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mtext>A</m:mtext><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mtext>[HA]</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idp39416656">þar sem styrkurinn er sá sem er við jafnvægi. Þrátt fyrir að vatn sé hvarfefni í efnahvarfinu er það einnig leysirinn, þannig að við tökum [H<sub>2</sub>O] ekki með í jöfnunni. Því stærra sem <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>a</sub> sýru er, því stærri er styrkur <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:msup><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> og A<sup>−</sup> miðað við styrk ójónuðu sýrunnar, HA, í jafnvægisblöndu, og því sterkari er sýran. Sýra er flokkuð sem „sterk“ þegar hún gengst undir fullkomna jónun, en í því tilfelli er styrkur HA núll og sýrujónunarfastinn ómælanlega stór (<emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>a</sub> ≈ ∞). Sýrur sem jónast að hluta eru kallaðar „veikar“ og hægt er að mæla sýrujónunarfastann þeirra með tilraunum. Tafla yfir jónunarfastar fyrir veikar sýrur er í <link document="m68866">Appendix H</link>.</para>
<para id="fs-idm220763536">Til að útskýra þessa hugmynd eru þrjár sýrujónunarjöfnur og <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>a</sub> gildi sýnd hér að neðan. Jónunarfastarnir aukast frá fyrstu til síðustu jöfnunnar sem taldar eru upp, sem gefur til kynna að hlutfallslegur sýrustyrkur aukist í röðinni CH<sub>3</sub>CO<sub>2</sub>H &lt; HNO<sub>2</sub> &lt; <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>HSO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>:</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<equation id="fs-idp100550608" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>l</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:msup><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="5em"/><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>a</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1.8</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−5</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<equation id="fs-idm57962960" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>HNO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>l</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:msup><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="5em"/><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>a</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4.6</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−4</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<equation id="fs-idm223507040" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>HSO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:msup><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>SO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mrow><m:mn>2−</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="5em"/><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>a</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1.2</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idm115717600">Annar mælikvarði á styrk sýru er jónunarprósenta hennar. <term id="term-00002">Jónunarprósenta (e. percent ionization)</term> veikrar sýru er skilgreind út frá samsetningu jafnvægisblöndu:</para>
<equation id="fs-idm149756192" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>% ionization</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:msup><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mtext>eq</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mtext>HA]</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:msub></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mn>100</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idm163389088">þar sem teljarinn jafngildir styrk samoka basa sýrunnar (samkvæmt efnajöfnuhlutfalli, [A<sup>−</sup>] = [H<sub>3</sub>O<sup>+</sup>]). Ólíkt <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>a</sub> gildinu breytist jónunarprósenta veikrar sýru með upphafsstyrk sýrunnar og minnkar yfirleitt þegar styrkurinn eykst. Hægt er að nota jafnvægisútreikninga af því tagi sem lýst er síðar í þessum kafla til að staðfesta þessa hegðun.</para>
<example id="fs-idm163336240">
<para id="fs-idp45762800"><title>Útreikningur á jónunarprósentu út frá pH</title>Reiknaðu jónunarprósentu 0,125-<emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> lausnar af saltpéturssýrlingi (veik sýra), með pH 2,09.</para>
<para id="fs-idm95442560"><title>Lausn</title>Jónunarprósentan fyrir sýru er:</para>
<equation id="fs-idm119459936" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:msup><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mtext>eq</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>HNO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:msub></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mn>100</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idm68557120">Með því að breyta uppgefnu pH-gildi í mólstyrk hýdróníumjóna fæst</para>
<equation id="fs-idm173125616" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mo>+</m:mo></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>2.09</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0.0081</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mi>M</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idm213993776">Með því að setja þetta gildi og uppgefinn upphafsstyrk sýrunnar inn í jöfnuna fyrir jónunarprósentu fæst</para>
<equation id="fs-idm83770448" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>8.1</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>0.125</m:mn></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mn>100</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>6.5</m:mn><m:mi>%</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idp164624">(Mundu að uppgefið pH-gildi 2,09 er logragildi og inniheldur því aðeins tvo markverða stafi, sem takmarkar nákvæmni útreiknaðrar jónunarprósentu.)</para>
<para id="fs-idp51316352"><title>Kannaðu þekkingu þína</title>Reiknaðu jónunarprósentu 0,10-<emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> lausnar af ediksýru með pH 2,89.</para>
<note id="fs-idp9633456">
<title>Answer:</title>
<para id="fs-idm119453808">1,3% jónuð</para>
</note>
</example>
<note id="fs-idp45486128" class="chemistry link-to-learning">
<para id="fs-idm98260672">Skoðaðu <link url="http://openstax.org/l/16AcidBase">hermunina</link> á sterkum og veikum sýrum og bösum á sameindastigi.</para>
</note>
<para id="fs-idm98628800">Rétt eins og fyrir sýrur endurspeglast hlutfallslegur styrkur basa í stærðargráðu <term id="term-00003">basajónunarfastans (<emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>b</sub>) (e. base-ionization constant (kb))</term> í vatnslausnum. Í lausnum með sama styrk jónast sterkari basar í meira mæli og gefa því hærri styrk hýdroxíðjóna en veikari basar. Sterkari basi hefur stærri jónunarfastann en veikari basi. Fyrir efnahvarf basa, B:</para>
<equation id="fs-idm69456656" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>B</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>l</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>HB</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>,</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idp1182192">er jónunarfastinn skrifaður sem</para>
<equation id="fs-idm72726864" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>b</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>HB</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mo>]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>[</m:mo><m:mtext>B</m:mtext><m:mo>]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idp86117152">Skoðun á gögnum fyrir þrjá veika basa sem sýndir eru hér að neðan sýnir að basastyrkurinn eykst í röðinni <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mo>−</m:mo></m:msup><m:mo>&lt;</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mo>−</m:mo></m:msup><m:mo>&lt;</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo>.</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<equation id="fs-idm168482736" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mtable><m:mtr><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>l</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>HNO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mtd><m:mtd/><m:mtd columnalign="right"><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>b</m:mtext></m:msub></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mo>=</m:mo></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mn>2.17</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−11</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mtd></m:mtr>
<m:mtr><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>l</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mtd><m:mtd/><m:mtd columnalign="right"><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>b</m:mtext></m:msub></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mo>=</m:mo></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mn>5.6</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−10</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mtd></m:mtr>
<m:mtr><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>l</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mtd><m:mtd/><m:mtd columnalign="right"><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>b</m:mtext></m:msub></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mo>=</m:mo></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mn>1.8</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−5</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mtd></m:mtr></m:mtable></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idm69273568">Tafla yfir jónunarfasta veikra basa er í <link document="m68867">Appendix I</link>. Eins og með sýrur endurspeglast hlutfallslegur styrkur basa einnig í jónunarprósentu hans, sem er reiknuð sem</para>
<equation id="fs-idm208527632" class="unnumbered"><m:math>
<m:mrow>
<m:mi>%</m:mi><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mtext>ionization</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msub>
<m:mrow>
<m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup>
<m:mrow>
<m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow>
<m:mtext>−</m:mtext>
</m:msup>
<m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow>
<m:mrow>
<m:mi>e</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi></m:mrow>
</m:msub>
<m:mtext>/</m:mtext><m:msub>
<m:mrow>
<m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mtext>B</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow>
<m:mn>0</m:mn>
</m:msub>
<m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>100</m:mn><m:mi>%</m:mi></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idm475449120">en hún er breytileg eftir jónunarfasta basans og upphafsstyrk lausnarinnar.</para>
</section>
<section id="fs-idm178559536">
<title>Hlutfallslegur styrkur samoka sýru-basa para</title>
<para id="fs-idm172520016">Brønsted-Lowry sýru-basa efnafræði snýst um flutning róteinda; því bendir rökfræðin til þess að samband sé á milli hlutfallslegs styrks samoka sýru-basa para. Styrkur sýru eða basa er magngreindur í jónunarfasta hennar, <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>a</sub> eða <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>b</sub>, sem táknar umfang jónunarhvarfs sýrunnar eða basans. Fyrir samoka sýru-basa parið HA / A<sup>−</sup> eru jafnvægisjónunarjöfnurnar og jónunarfastajöfnurnar:</para>
<equation id="fs-idm157208576" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>HA</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>l</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:msup><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mtext>A</m:mtext><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="5em"/><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>a</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:msup><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mtext>A</m:mtext><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mo>]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mtext>HA</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mo>]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<equation id="fs-idm215792928" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mtext>A</m:mtext><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>l</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mtext>HA</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="5em"/><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>b</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mtext>HA</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mo>]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext><m:mo>–</m:mo></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mo>]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mtext>A</m:mtext><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mo>]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idm217883488">Með því að leggja saman þessar tvær efnafræðijöfnur fæst jafnan fyrir sjálfjónun vatns:</para>
<equation id="fs-idp71522608" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:menclose notation="horizontalstrike"><m:mrow><m:mtext>HA(</m:mtext><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:menclose><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>l</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:menclose notation="horizontalstrike"><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mtext>A</m:mtext><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:menclose><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>l</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:msup><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:menclose notation="horizontalstrike"><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mtext>A</m:mtext><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:menclose><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:menclose notation="horizontalstrike"><m:mrow><m:mtext>HA(</m:mtext><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:menclose></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<equation id="fs-idm122391632" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>2H</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>l</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:msup><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idm160491872">Eins og fjallað var um í öðrum kafla um jafnvægi er jafnvægisfastinn fyrir samanlagt efnahvarf jafngildur stærðfræðilegu margfeldi jafnvægisfasta fyrir efnahvörfin sem lögð eru saman, og því</para>
<equation id="fs-idm141982832" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>a</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>b</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:msup><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mtext>A</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mtext>[HA]</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mtext>[HA]</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mo>]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mtext>A</m:mtext><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mo>]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:msup><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mo>]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>w</m:mtext></m:msub></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idm224463760">Þessi jafna lýsir sambandinu milli jónunarfasta fyrir hvaða samoka sýru-basa par sem er, nefnilega að stærðfræðilegt margfeldi þeirra er jafnt jónamargfeldi vatns, <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>w</sub>. Með því að endurraða þessari jöfnu verður andhverft samband milli styrks samoka sýru-basa pars augljóst:</para>
<equation id="fs-idm223919584" class="unnumbered"><m:math>
<m:mrow>
<m:msub>
<m:mi>K</m:mi>
<m:mtext>a</m:mtext>
</m:msub>
<m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msub>
<m:mi>K</m:mi>
<m:mtext>w</m:mtext>
</m:msub>
<m:mtext>/</m:mtext><m:msub>
<m:mi>K</m:mi>
<m:mtext>b</m:mtext>
</m:msub>
<m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mtext>or</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msub>
<m:mi>K</m:mi>
<m:mtext>b</m:mtext>
</m:msub>
<m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msub>
<m:mi>K</m:mi>
<m:mtext>w</m:mtext>
</m:msub>
<m:mtext>/</m:mtext><m:msub>
<m:mi>K</m:mi>
<m:mtext>a</m:mtext>
</m:msub>
</m:mrow>
</m:math>
</equation>
<para id="fs-idm225241056">Andhverfa hlutfallssambandið milli <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>a</sub> og <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>b</sub> þýðir að <emphasis effect="italics">því sterkari sem sýran eða basinn er, því veikari er samoka maki hennar</emphasis>. <link target-id="CNX_Chem_14_03_strengths"/> sýnir þetta samband fyrir nokkur samoka sýru-basa pör.</para>
<figure id="CNX_Chem_14_03_strengths">
<media id="fs-idm162584688" alt="The diagram shows two horizontal bars. The first, labeled, “Relative acid strength,” at the top is red on the left and gradually changes to purple on the right. The red end at the left is labeled, “Stronger acids.” The purple end at the right is labeled, “Weaker acids.” Just outside the bar to the lower left is the label, “K subscript a.” The bar is marked off in increments with a specific acid listed above each increment. The first mark is at 1.0 with H subscript 3 O superscript positive sign. The second is ten raised to the negative two with H C l O subscript 2. The third is ten raised to the negative 4 with H F. The fourth is ten raised to the negative 6 with H subscript 2 C O subscript 3. The fifth is ten raised to a negative 8 with C H subscript 3 C O O H. The sixth is ten raised to the negative ten with N H subscript 4 superscript positive sign. The seventh is ten raised to a negative 12 with H P O subscript 4 superscript 2 negative sign. The eighth is ten raised to the negative 14 with H subscript 2 O. Similarly the second bar, which is labeled “Relative conjugate base strength,” is purple at the left end and gradually becomes blue at the right end. Outside the bar to the left is the label, “Weaker bases.” Outside the bar to the right is the label, “Stronger bases.” Below and to the left of the bar is the label, “K subscript b.” The bar is similarly marked at increments with bases listed above each increment. The first is at ten raised to the negative 14 with H subscript 2 O above it. The second is ten raised to the negative 12 C l O subscript 2 superscript negative sign. The third is ten raised to the negative ten with F superscript negative sign. The fourth is ten raised to a negative eight with H C O subscript 3 superscript negative sign. The fifth is ten raised to the negative 6 with C H subscript 3 C O O superscript negative sign. The sixth is ten raised to the negative 4 with N H subscript 3. The seventh is ten raised to the negative 2 with P O subscript 4 superscript three negative sign. The eighth is 1.0 with O H superscript negative sign.">
<image mime-type="image/jpeg" src="../../media/CNX_Chem_14_03_strengths.jpg"/>
</media>
<caption>Hlutfallslegur styrkur nokkurra samoka sýru-basa para er sýndur.</caption>
</figure>
<figure id="CNX_Chem_14_03_Corresp"><media id="fs-idm44354768" alt="This figure includes a table separated into a left half which is labeled “Acids” and a right half labeled “Bases.” A red arrow points up the left side, which is labeled “Increasing acid strength.” Similarly, a blue arrow points downward along the right side, which is labeled “Increasing base strength.” Names of acids and bases are listed next to each arrow toward the center of the table, followed by chemical formulas. Acids listed top to bottom are sulfuric acid, H subscript 2 S O subscript 4, hydrogen iodide, H I, hydrogen bromide, H B r, hydrogen chloride, H C l, nitric acid, H N O subscript 3, hydronium ion ( in pink text) H subscript 3 O superscript plus, hydrogen sulfate ion, H S O subscript 4 superscript negative, phosphoric acid, H subscript 3 P O subscript 4, hydrogen fluoride, H F, nitrous acid, H N O subscript 2, acetic acid, C H subscript 3 C O subscript 2 H, carbonic acid H subscript 2 C O subscript 3, hydrogen sulfide, H subscript 2 S, ammonium ion, N H subscript 4 superscript +, hydrogen cyanide, H C N, hydrogen carbonate ion, H C O subscript 3 superscript negative, water (shaded in beige) H subscript 2 O, hydrogen sulfide ion, H S superscript negative, ethanol, C subscript 2 H subscript 5 O H, ammonia, N H subscript 3, hydrogen, H subscript 2, methane, and C H subscript 4. The acids at the top of the listing from sulfuric acid through nitric acid are grouped with a bracket to the right labeled “Undergo complete acid ionization in water.” Similarly, the acids at the bottom from hydrogen sulfide ion through methane are grouped with a bracket and labeled, “Do not undergo acid ionization in water.” The right half of the figure lists bases and formulas. From top to bottom the bases listed are hydrogen sulfate ion, H S O subscript 4 superscript negative, iodide ion, I superscript negative, bromide ion, B r superscript negative, chloride ion, C l superscript negative, nitrate ion, N O subscript 3 superscript negative, water (shaded in beige), H subscript 2 O, sulfate ion, S O subscript 4 superscript 2 negative, dihydrogen phosphate ion, H subscript 2 P O subscript 4 superscript negative, fluoride ion, F superscript negative, nitrite ion, N O subscript 2 superscript negative, acetate ion, C H subscript 3 C O subscript 2 superscript negative, hydrogen carbonate ion, H C O subscript 3 superscript negative, hydrogen sulfide ion, H S superscript negative, ammonia, N H subscript 3, cyanide ion, C N superscript negative, carbonate ion, C O subscript 3 superscript 2 negative, hydroxide ion (in blue), O H superscript negative, sulfide ion, S superscript 2 negative, ethoxide ion, C subscript 2 H subscript 5 O superscript negative, amide ion N H subscript 2 superscript negative, hydride ion, H superscript negative, and methide ion C H subscript 3 superscript negative. The bases at the top, from perchlorate ion through nitrate ion are group with a bracket which is labeled “Do not undergo base ionization in water.” Similarly, the lower 5 in the listing, from sulfide ion through methide ion are grouped and labeled “Undergo complete base ionization in water.”">
<image mime-type="image/jpeg" src="../../media/CNX_Chem_14_03_corresp.jpg"/>
</media>
<caption>Þessi mynd sýnir styrk samoka sýru-basa para í hlutfalli við styrk vatns sem viðmiðunarefnis.</caption></figure>
<para id="fs-idm225187616">Listinn yfir samoka sýru-basa pör sem sýndur er í <link target-id="CNX_Chem_14_03_Corresp"/> er raðað til að sýna hlutfallslegan styrk hverrar efnategundar samanborið við vatn, en færslur þess eru auðkenndar í báðum dálkum töflunnar. Í sýrudálkinum eru þær efnategundir sem eru skráðar fyrir neðan vatn veikari sýrur en vatn. Þessar efnategundir gangast ekki undir sýrujónun í vatni; þær eru ekki Brønsted-Lowry sýrur. Allar efnategundir sem skráðar eru fyrir ofan vatn eru sterkari sýrur, sem flytja róteindir yfir á vatn að einhverju leyti þegar þær eru leystar upp í vatnslausn til að mynda hýdróníumjónir. Efnategundir fyrir ofan vatn en fyrir neðan hýdróníumjón eru <emphasis effect="italics">veikar sýrur</emphasis>, sem gangast undir að hluta til sýrujónun, en þær sem eru fyrir ofan hýdróníumjón eru <emphasis effect="italics">sterkar sýrur</emphasis> sem eru fullkomlega jónaðar í vatnslausn.</para>
<para id="fs-idm213445440">Ef allar þessar sterku sýrur eru fullkomlega jónaðar í vatni, hvers vegna gefur dálkurinn til kynna að styrkur þeirra sé breytilegur, þar sem saltpéturssýra er veikust og perklórsýra sterkust? Taktu eftir að eina sýrutegundin sem er til staðar í vatnslausn af hvaða sterkri sýru sem er, er H<sub>3</sub>O<sup>+</sup>(<emphasis effect="italics">aq</emphasis>), sem þýðir að hýdróníumjón er sterkasta sýran sem getur verið til í vatni; sérhver sterkari sýra mun hvarfast fullkomlega við vatn til að mynda hýdróníumjónir. Þessi takmörkun á sýrustyrk uppleystra efna í lausn er kölluð <emphasis effect="bold">jafnandi áhrif</emphasis>. Til að mæla muninn á sýrustyrk „sterkra“ sýra verður að leysa sýrurnar upp í leysi sem er <emphasis effect="italics">minna basískur</emphasis> en vatn. Í slíkum leysum verða sýrurnar „veikar“ og því er hægt að ákvarða hvers kyns mun á umfangi jónunar þeirra. Til dæmis eru tvíundarvetnishalíðin HCl, HBr og HI sterkar sýrur í vatni en veikar sýrur í etanóli (styrkur eykst HCl &lt; HBr &lt; HI).</para>
<para id="fs-idm167383056">Hægri dálkurinn í <link target-id="CNX_Chem_14_03_Corresp"/> telur upp fjölda efna í röð vaxandi basastyrks frá toppi til botns. Samkvæmt sömu rökfræði og fyrir vinstri dálkinn eru efnategundir sem skráðar eru fyrir ofan vatn veikari basar og gangast því ekki undir basajónun þegar þær eru leystar upp í vatni. Efnategundir sem skráðar eru á milli vatns og samoka basa þess, hýdroxíðjónar, eru veikir basar sem jónast að hluta. Efnategundir sem skráðar eru fyrir neðan hýdroxíðjón eru sterkir basar sem jónast fullkomlega í vatni til að gefa hýdroxíðjónir (þ.e. þær eru <emphasis effect="italics">jafnaðar</emphasis> við hýdroxíð). Samanburður á sýru- og basadálkunum í þessari töflu styður andhverfa sambandið milli styrks samoka sýru-basa para. Til dæmis eru samoka basar sterkra sýra (efst í töflunni) allir með hverfandi styrk. Sterk sýra sýnir ómælanlega stóran <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>a</sub>, og því mun samoka basi hennar sýna <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>b</sub> sem er í raun núll:</para>
<para id="fs-idm200218096"><m:math>
<m:mtable columnalign="left">
<m:mtr>
<m:mtd>
<m:mtext>strong</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mtext>acid</m:mtext><m:mo>:</m:mo><m:mspace width="5em"/><m:msub>
<m:mi>K</m:mi>
<m:mtext>a</m:mtext>
</m:msub>
<m:mo>≈</m:mo><m:mi>∞</m:mi>
</m:mtd>
</m:mtr>
<m:mtr>
<m:mtd>
<m:mtext>conjugate</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mtext>base</m:mtext><m:mo>:</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msub>
<m:mi>K</m:mi>
<m:mtext>b</m:mtext>
</m:msub>
<m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msub>
<m:mi>K</m:mi>
<m:mtext>w</m:mtext>
</m:msub>
<m:mtext>/</m:mtext><m:msub>
<m:mi>K</m:mi>
<m:mtext>a</m:mtext>
</m:msub>
<m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msub>
<m:mi>K</m:mi>
<m:mtext>w</m:mtext>
</m:msub>
<m:mtext>/</m:mtext><m:mi>∞</m:mi><m:mo>≈</m:mo><m:mn>0</m:mn>
</m:mtd>
</m:mtr>
</m:mtable>
</m:math></para>
<para id="fs-idm225937888">Svipaða nálgun má nota til að styðja þá athugun að samoka sýrur sterkra basa (<emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>b</sub> ≈ ∞) séu af hverfandi styrk (<emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>a</sub> ≈ 0).</para>
<example id="fs-idp2197392">
<para id="fs-idm154506736"><title>Útreikningur jónunarfasta fyrir samoka sýru-basa pör</title>Notaðu <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>b</sub> fyrir nítrítjónina, <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>,</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> til að reikna út <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>a</sub> fyrir samoka sýru hennar.</para>
<para id="fs-idm172466976"><title>Lausn</title><emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>b</sub> fyrir <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> er gefið í þessum kafla sem 2,17 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−11</sup>. Samoka sýra <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> er HNO<sub>2</sub>; <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>a</sub> fyrir HNO<sub>2</sub> er hægt að reikna út með því að nota sambandið:</para><equation id="fs-idm197198576" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>a</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>b</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1.0</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−14</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>w</m:mtext></m:msub></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idm174350000">Með því að leysa fyrir <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>a</sub> fæst</para>
<equation id="fs-idp100620656" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>a</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>w</m:mtext></m:msub></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>b</m:mtext></m:msub></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>1.0</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−14</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>2.17</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mn>−11</m:mn></m:msup></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4.6</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−4</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></equation><para id="fs-idm122128048">Þetta svar má staðfesta með því að finna <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>a</sub> fyrir HNO<sub>2</sub> í <link document="m68866">Appendix H</link>.</para>
<para id="fs-idp28811616"><title>Kannaðu þekkingu þína</title>Ákvarðaðu hlutfallslegan sýrustyrk <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> og HCN með því að bera saman jónunarfastana þeirra. Jónunarfasti HCN er gefinn í <link document="m68866">Appendix H</link> sem 4,9 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−10</sup>. Jónunarfasti <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> er ekki skráður, en jónunarfasti samoka basa þess, NH<sub>3</sub>, er skráður sem 1,8 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−5</sup>.</para>
<note id="fs-idp12994032">
<title>Answer:</title>
<para id="fs-idm80300528"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> er örlítið sterkari sýran (<emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>a</sub> fyrir <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> = 5,6 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−10</sup>).</para>
</note>
</example>
</section>
<section id="fs-idm160956208">
<title>Útreikningar á sýru-basa jafnvægi</title>
<para id="fs-idm226989136">Í kaflanum um efnajafnvægi voru kynntar nokkrar gerðir jafnvægisútreikninga og ýmsar stærðfræðilegar aðferðir sem eru gagnlegar við framkvæmd þeirra. Þessar aðferðir eru almennt gagnlegar fyrir jafnvægiskerfi óháð flokki efnahvarfa og því má beita þeim á áhrifaríkan hátt á sýru-basa jafnvægisvandamál. Í þessum kafla eru kynnt nokkur dæmi um æfingar sem fela í sér jafnvægisútreikninga fyrir sýru-basa kerfi.</para>
<media id="fs-idp23785056" class="scaled-down" alt="This image shows two bottles containing clear colorless solutions. Each bottle contains a single p H indicator strip. The strip in the bottle on the left is red, and a similar red strip is placed on a filter paper circle in front of the bottle on surface on which the bottles are resting. Similarly, the second bottle on the right contains and orange strip and an orange strip is placed in front of it on a filter paper circle. Between the two bottles is a pack of p Hydrion papers with a p H color scale on its cover.">
<image mime-type="image/jpeg" src="../../media/CNX_Chem_14_03_acetate_img.jpg"/>
</media>
<media id="fs-idm134302736" class="scaled-down" alt="This photo shows two glass containers filled with a transparent liquid. In between the containers is a p H strip indicator guide. There are p H strips placed in front of each glass container. The liquid in the container on the left appears to have a p H of 10 or 11. The liquid in the container on the right appears to have a p H of about 13 or 14.">
<image mime-type="image/jpeg" src="../../media/CNX_Chem_14_03_ammonia.jpg"/>
</media>
<example id="fs-idm223269056">
<para id="fs-idm118702752"><title>Ákvörðun <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>a</sub> út frá jafnvægisstyrk</title>Ediksýra er aðalefnið í ediki (<link target-id="CNX_Chem_14_03_Vinegar"/>) sem gefur því súrt bragð. Við jafnvægi inniheldur lausn [CH<sub>3</sub>CO<sub>2</sub>H] = 0,0787 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> og <m:math><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:msup><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0.00118</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mi>M</m:mi><m:mo>.</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> Hvert er gildi <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>a</sub> fyrir ediksýru?</para>
<!-- figure handled separately -->
<para id="fs-idm119280448"><title>Lausn</title>Viðeigandi jafnvægisjafna og jafnvægisfastastæða hennar eru sýndar hér að neðan. Með því að setja inn uppgefinn jafnvægisstyrk er hægt að framkvæma einfaldan útreikning á <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>a</sub> fyrir ediksýru.</para>
<equation id="fs-idp69048880" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>l</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:msup><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<equation id="fs-idm77961248" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>a</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:msup><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mn>0.00118</m:mn><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mn>0.00118</m:mn><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>0.0787</m:mn></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1.77</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−5</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idm68555680"><title>Kannaðu þekkingu þína</title><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>HSO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> jónin, veik sýra sem notuð er í sum hreinsiefni fyrir heimili:</para>
<equation id="fs-idm174702176" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>HSO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>l</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:msup><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>SO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mrow><m:mn>2−</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idm168960944">Hver er sýrujónunarfastinn fyrir þessa veiku sýru ef jafnvægisblanda hefur eftirfarandi samsetningu: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:msup><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> = 0,027 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>; <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>HSO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0.29</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mi>M</m:mi><m:mo>;</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> og <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>SO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mrow><m:mn>2−</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0.13</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mi>M</m:mi><m:mo>?</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<note id="fs-idp348400">
<title>Answer:</title>
<para id="fs-idp1308432"><emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>a</sub> fyrir <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>HSO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> = 1,2 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−2</sup></para>
</note>
</example>
<figure id="CNX_Chem_14_03_Vinegar" class="scaled-down">
<media id="fs-idm137777920" alt="An image shows the label of a bottle of distilled white vinegar. The label states that the contents have been reduced with water to 5 percent acidity.">
<image mime-type="image/jpeg" src="../../media/CNX_Chem_14_03_Vinegar.jpg"/>
</media>
<caption>Edik inniheldur ediksýru, sem er veik sýra. (heimild: breyting á verki eftir „HomeSpot HQ“/Flickr)</caption>
</figure>
<example id="fs-idm154542240">
<para id="fs-idm1585392"><title>Ákvörðun <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>b</sub> út frá jafnvægisstyrk</title>Koffín, C<sub>8</sub>H<sub>10</sub>N<sub>4</sub>O<sub>2</sub>, er veikur basi. Hvert er gildi <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>b</sub> fyrir koffín ef lausn við jafnvægi hefur [C<sub>8</sub>H<sub>10</sub>N<sub>4</sub>O<sub>2</sub>] = 0,050 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>C</m:mtext><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mtext>N</m:mtext><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> = 5,0 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−3</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> og [OH<sup>−</sup>] = 2,5 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−3</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>?</para>
<para id="fs-idm64959408"><title>Lausn</title>Viðeigandi jafnvægisjafna og jafnvægisfastastæða hennar eru sýndar hér að neðan. Með því að setja inn uppgefinn jafnvægisstyrk er hægt að framkvæma einfaldan útreikning á <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>b</sub> fyrir koffín.</para>
<equation id="fs-idp57095280" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mtext>C</m:mtext><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mtext>N</m:mtext><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>l</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msub><m:mtext>C</m:mtext><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mtext>N</m:mtext><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<equation id="fs-idm114814304" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>b</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>C</m:mtext><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mtext>N</m:mtext><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mtext>C</m:mtext><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mtext>N</m:mtext><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mn>5.0</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mn>2.5</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>0.050</m:mn></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2.5</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−4</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idm122074528"><title>Kannaðu þekkingu þína</title>Hver er jafnvægisfastinn fyrir jónun <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>HPO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mrow><m:mn>2−</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> jónarinnar, sem er veikur basi</para>
<equation id="fs-idm98055840" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>HPO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mrow><m:mn>2−</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>l</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>PO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idp31344880">ef samsetning jafnvægisblöndu er sem hér segir: [OH<sup>−</sup>] = 1,3 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−6</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>; <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>PO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0.042</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mi>M</m:mi><m:mo>;</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> og <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>HPO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mrow><m:mn>2−</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0.341</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mi>M</m:mi><m:mo>?</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<note id="fs-idm157882608">
<title>Answer:</title>
<para id="fs-idp68248832"><emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>b</sub> fyrir <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>HPO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mrow><m:mn>2−</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1.6</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−7</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></para>
</note>
</example>
<example id="fs-idm1433984"><para id="fs-idm1433728"><title>Ákvörðun <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>a</sub> eða <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>b</sub> út frá pH</title>pH-gildi 0,0516-<emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> lausnar af saltpéturssýrlingi, HNO<sub>2</sub>, er 2,34. Hver er <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>a</sub>-fasti hennar?</para>
<equation id="fs-idp31767264" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>HNO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>l</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:msup><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idm163708144"><title>Lausn</title>Styrkur saltpéturssýrlingsins sem gefinn er upp er <emphasis effect="italics">formlegur</emphasis> styrkur, sem tekur ekki tillit til neins efnafræðilegs jafnvægis sem kann að myndast í lausninni. Slíkir styrkir eru meðhöndlaðir sem „upphafsgildi“ fyrir jafnvægisútreikninga með því að nota ICE-töfluaðferðina. Taktu eftir að upphafsgildi hýdróníumjónar er skráð sem <emphasis effect="italics">nálægt</emphasis> núlli vegna þess að lítill styrkur H<sub>3</sub>O<sup>+</sup> er til staðar (1 × 10<sup>−7</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>) vegna sjálfsjónunar vatns. Í mörgum tilfellum, eins og öllum þeim sem kynnt eru í þessum kafla, er þessi styrkur mun minni en sá sem myndast við jónun sýrunnar (eða basans) sem um ræðir og má því vanrækja hann.</para>
<para id="fs-idm204817712">pH-gildið sem gefið er upp er logaritmískur mælikvarði á styrk hýdróníumjóna sem myndast við sýrujónun saltpéturssýrlingsins og táknar því „jafnvægisgildi“ fyrir ICE-töfluna:</para>
<equation id="fs-idm219759136" class="unnumbered"><m:math>
<m:mrow>
<m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub>
<m:mtext>H</m:mtext>
<m:mn>3</m:mn>
</m:msub>
<m:msup>
<m:mtext>O</m:mtext>
<m:mo>+</m:mo>
</m:msup>
<m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msup>
<m:mrow>
<m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow>
<m:mrow>
<m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>2.34</m:mn></m:mrow>
</m:msup>
<m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0.0046</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mi>M</m:mi></m:mrow>
</m:math>
</equation>
<para id="fs-idm214144400">ICE-taflan fyrir þetta kerfi er þá</para>
<media id="fs-idm79844096" alt="This table has two main columns and four rows. The first row for the first column does not have a heading and then has the following in the first column: Initial concentration ( M ), Change ( M ), Equilibrium concentration ( M ). The second column has the header of “H N O subscript 2 plus sign H subscript 2 O equilibrium sign H subscript 3 O superscript positive sign plus sign N O subscript 2 superscript negative sign.” Under the second column is a subgroup of four columns and three rows. The first column has the following: 0.0516, negative 0.0046, 0.0470. The second column is blank in all three rows. The third column has the following: approximately 0, positive 0.0046, 0.0046. The fourth column has the following: 0, positive 0.0046, 0.0046." class="scaled-down">
<image mime-type="image/jpeg" src="../../media/CNX_Chem_14_03_ICETable2_img.jpg"/>
</media>
<para id="fs-idm98416272">Að lokum skaltu reikna út gildi jafnvægisfastans með því að nota gögnin í töflunni:</para>
<equation id="fs-idm98415888" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>a</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:msup><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>HNO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mn>0.0046</m:mn><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mn>0.0046</m:mn><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mn>0.0470</m:mn><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4.6</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−4</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idm166688304"><title>Kannaðu þekkingu þína.</title>pH-gildi lausnar af heimilisammoníaki, 0,950-<emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> lausn af NH<sub>3,</sub> er 11,612. Hver er <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>b</sub> fyrir NH<sub>3</sub>.</para>
<note id="fs-idm56490624">
<title>Answer:</title>
<para id="fs-idm56489984"><emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>b</sub> = 1,8 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−5</sup></para>
</note>
</example>
<example id="fs-idm159829376"><para id="fs-idm159829120"><title>Útreikningur á jafnvægisstyrk í lausn veikrar sýru</title>Maurasýra, HCO<sub>2</sub>H, er eitt af ertandi efnunum sem veldur viðbrögðum líkamans við sumum maurabitum og -stungum (<link target-id="CNX_Chem_14_03_AntSting"/>).</para>
<!-- figure handled separately -->
<para id="fs-idm94058112">Hver er styrkur hýdróníumjóna og pH-gildi 0,534-<emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> lausnar af maurasýru?</para>
<equation id="fs-idm83702544" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>HCO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>l</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:msup><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>HCO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="5em"/><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>a</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1.8</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−4</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idm42704112"><title>Lausn</title></para>
<para id="fs-idm475800144">ICE-taflan fyrir þetta kerfi er</para>
<media id="fs-idm3940608" alt="This table has two main columns and four rows. The first row for the first column does not have a heading and then has the following in the first column: Initial concentration ( M ), Change ( M ), Equilibrium concentration ( M ). The second column has the header of “H C O subscript 2 H plus sign H subscript 2 O equilibrium arrow H subscript 3 O superscript positive sign.” Under the second column is a subgroup of four columns and three rows. The first column has the following: 0.534, blank, 0.534 minus x. The second column is blank in all three rows. The third column has the following: approximately 0, positive x, x. The fourth column has the following: 0, positive x, x." class="scaled-down">
<image mime-type="image/jpeg" src="../../media/CNX_Chem_14_03_ICETable3_img.jpg"/>
</media>
<para id="fs-idm467257104">Með því að setja jafnvægisstyrksliðina inn í <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>a</sub>-segðina fæst<newline/> <equation id="fs-idm121323008" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>a</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1.8</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−4</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:msup><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>HCO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>HCO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math></equation><newline/> <equation id="fs-idm121316224" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>0.534</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1.8</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−4</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></equation><newline/> Tiltölulega hár upphafsstyrkur og lítill jafnvægisfasti leyfa þá einföldunarforsendu að <emphasis effect="italics">x</emphasis> verði mun minna en 0,534 og því verður jafnan<newline/> <equation id="fs-idp29061504" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>a</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1.8</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−4</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mtext>2</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>0.534</m:mn></m:mrow></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math></equation><newline/> Með því að leysa jöfnuna fyrir <emphasis effect="italics">x</emphasis> fæst<newline/> <equation id="fs-idp107591296" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mtext>2</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0.534</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mn>1.8</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−4</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>9.6</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.4em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.4em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−5</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></equation><newline/> <equation id="fs-idm94907344" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mrow><m:mn>9.6</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−5</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math></equation><newline/> <equation id="fs-idp49583344" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>9.8</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mi>M</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math></equation></para>
<para id="fs-idp83161504">Til að kanna forsenduna um að <emphasis effect="italics">x</emphasis> sé lítið í samanburði við 0,534 er hægt að meta hlutfallslega stærð þess:</para>
<equation id="fs-idp83162400" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mn>0.534</m:mn></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>9.8</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>0.534</m:mn></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1.8</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mn>1.8</m:mn><m:mi>%</m:mi><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mtext>of 0.534</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idp87107328">Vegna þess að <emphasis effect="italics">x</emphasis> er minna en 5% af upphafsstyrknum er forsendan gild.</para>
<para id="fs-idm490302912">Eins og skilgreint er í ICE-töflunni er <emphasis effect="italics">x</emphasis> jafnt og jafnvægisstyrkur hýdróníumjónar:</para>
<equation id="fs-idm212466048" class="unnumbered"><m:math>
<m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub>
<m:mtext>H</m:mtext>
<m:mn>3</m:mn>
</m:msub>
<m:msup>
<m:mtext>O</m:mtext>
<m:mo>+</m:mo>
</m:msup>
<m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0.0098</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mi>M</m:mi></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idm218699232">Að lokum er pH-gildið reiknað og fæst</para>
<equation id="fs-idm479799296" class="unnumbered"><m:math>
<m:mrow>
<m:mtext>pH</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>−</m:mtext><m:mtext>log</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub>
<m:mtext>H</m:mtext>
<m:mn>3</m:mn>
</m:msub>
<m:msup>
<m:mtext>O</m:mtext>
<m:mo>+</m:mo>
</m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>−</m:mtext><m:mtext>log</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mn>0.0098</m:mn><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2.01</m:mn></m:mrow>
</m:math>
</equation>
<para id="fs-idp80326224"><title>Kannaðu þekkingu þína</title>Aðeins lítill hluti veikrar sýru jónast í vatnslausn. Hver er jónunarprósenta 0,100-<emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> lausnar af ediksýru, CH<sub>3</sub>CO<sub>2</sub>H?</para>
<equation id="fs-idp80328288" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>l</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:msup><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="5em"/><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>a</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1.8</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−5</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<note id="fs-idp77192016">
<title>Answer:</title>
<para id="fs-idp77192656">jónunarprósenta = 1,3%</para>
</note>
</example>
<figure id="CNX_Chem_14_03_AntSting" class="scaled-down">
<media id="fs-idm94059808" alt="A photograph is shown of a large black ant on the end of a human finger.">
<image mime-type="image/jpeg" src="../../media/CNX_Chem_14_03_AntSting.jpg"/>
</media>
<caption>Sársaukinn af sumum maurabitum og -stungum stafar af maurasýru. (heimild: John Tann)</caption>
</figure>
<example id="fs-idp77193872">
<para id="fs-idp77194128"><title>Útreikningur á jafnvægisstyrk í lausn veiks basa</title>Finndu styrk hýdroxíðjónar, pOH og pH 0,25-<emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> lausnar af trímetýlamíni, sem er veikur basi:</para>
<equation id="fs-idm75350896" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>N</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>l</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>NH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="5em"/><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>b</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>6.3</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−5</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idp38644736"><title>Lausn</title>ICE-taflan fyrir þetta kerfi er<newline/> <media id="fs-idm115891984" class="scaled-down" alt="This table has two main columns and four rows. The first row for the first column does not have a heading and then has the following in the first column: Initial concentration ( M ), Change ( M ), Equilibrium concentration ( M ). The second column has the header of “( C H subscript 3 ) subscript 3 N plus sign H subscript 2 O equilibrium arrow ( C H subscript 3 ) subscript 3 N H superscript positive sign plus sign O H superscript positive sign.” Under the second column is a subgroup of four columns and three rows. The first column has the following: 0.25, negative x, 0.25 plus sign negative x. The second column is blank in all three rows. The third column has the following: 0, x, 0 plus x. The fourth column has the following: approximately 0, x, and approximately 0 plus x."><image mime-type="image/jpeg" src="../../media/CNX_Chem_14_03_ICETable4_img.jpg"/></media><newline/> Ef jafnvægisstyrkstölunum er stungið inn í jöfnuna fyrir <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>b</sub> fæst<newline/> <equation id="fs-idp121892160" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>b</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>NH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mo>]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>N</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>0.25</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>6.3</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−5</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></equation><newline/> Ef gert er ráð fyrir að <emphasis effect="italics">x</emphasis> &lt;&lt; 0,25 og leyst fyrir <emphasis effect="italics">x</emphasis> fæst<newline/> <equation id="fs-idm1664928" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4.0</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mi>M</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math></equation><newline/> Þetta gildi er minna en 5% af upphafsstyrknum (0,25), svo að nálgunin er réttlætanleg.<newline/> Eins og skilgreint er í ICE-töflunni er <emphasis effect="italics">x</emphasis> jafnt og jafnvægisstyrkur hýdroxíðjónarinnar:<newline/> <equation id="fs-idm79961072" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mo>]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>~</m:mo><m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4.0</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mi>M</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math></equation><newline/> <equation id="fs-idp50312800" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4.0</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mi>M</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math></equation><newline/> pOH er reiknað sem<newline/> <equation id="fs-idm73318512" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>pOH</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>−log</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mn>4.0</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2.40</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></equation><newline/> Með því að nota sambandið sem kynnt var í fyrri hluta þessa kafla:<newline/> <equation id="fs-idp50335856" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>pH</m:mtext><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mtext>pOH</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>p</m:mtext><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>w</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>14.00</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></equation><newline/> er hægt að reikna pH:<newline/> <equation id="fs-idp50339184" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>pH</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>14.00</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mtext>pOH</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>14.00</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>2.40</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>11.60</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></equation></para>
<para id="fs-idm83886080"><title>Kannaðu þekkingu þína</title>Reiknaðu styrk hýdroxíðjónar og jónunarprósentu 0,0325-<emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> lausnar af ammóníaki, veikum basa með <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>b</sub> = 1,76 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−5</sup>.</para>
<note id="fs-idp71571472">
<title>Answer:</title>
<para id="fs-idp71572112">7,56 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−4</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>, 2,33%</para>
</note>
</example>
<para id="fs-idm114523920">Í sumum tilfellum veldur styrkur veiku sýrunnar eða basans og formlegur (upphafs) styrkur þeirra umtalsverðri jónun. Þótt ICE-aðferðin sé enn áhrifarík fyrir þessi kerfi er algebran aðeins flóknari vegna þess að ekki er hægt að gera þá einföldun að <emphasis effect="italics">x</emphasis> sé hverfandi. Útreikningar af þessu tagi eru sýndir í <link target-id="fs-idm114522688"/> hér að neðan.</para>
<example id="fs-idm114522688">
<para id="fs-idm114522432"><title>Útreikningur jafnvægisstyrks án einföldunarforsendna</title>Natríumbísúlfat, NaHSO<sub>4</sub>, er notað í sum hreinsiefni fyrir heimili sem uppspretta <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>HSO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> jónarinnar, sem er veik sýra. Hvert er pH 0,50-<emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> lausnar af <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>HSO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>?</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math>?</para>
<equation id="fs-idm83628320" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>HSO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>l</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:msup><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>SO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mrow><m:mn>2−</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="5em"/><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>a</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1.2</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idp42421216"><title>Lausn</title>ICE-taflan fyrir þetta kerfi er<newline/> <media id="fs-idm4774976" class="scaled-down" alt="This table has two main columns and four rows. The first row for the first column does not have a heading and then has the following in the first column: Initial concentration ( M ), Change ( M ), Equilibrium ( M ). The second column has the header of “H S O subscript 4 superscript negative sign plus sign H subscript 2 O equilibrium sign H subscript 3 O superscript positive sign plus sign S O subscript 4 superscript 2 superscript negative sign.” Under the second column is a subgroup of four columns and three rows. The first column has the following: 0.50, negative x, 0.50 minus x. The second column is blank for all three rows. The third column has the following: approximately 0, positive x, x. The fourth column has the following: 0, positive x, x."><image mime-type="image/jpeg" src="../../media/CNX_Chem_14_03_ICETable5_img.jpg"/></media><newline/> Ef jafnvægisstyrkstölunum er stungið inn í jöfnuna fyrir <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>a</sub> fæst<newline/> <equation id="fs-idp53226240" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>a</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1.2</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:msup><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>SO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mrow><m:mn>2−</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>HSO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>0.50</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mrow></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math></equation><newline/> Ef gert er ráð fyrir að <emphasis effect="italics">x</emphasis> &lt;&lt; 0,5, er jafnan hér að ofan einfölduð og leyst fyrir <emphasis effect="italics">x</emphasis> sem gefur<newline/> <equation id="fs-idm181668752" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0.077</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mi>M</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math></equation><newline/> Þetta gildi <emphasis effect="italics">x</emphasis> er augljóslega ekki marktækt minna en 0,50 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>; það er frekar um 15% af upphafsstyrknum:<newline/> Þegar við könnum forsenduna reiknum við:<newline/> <equation id="fs-idm97097488" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>HSO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mtext>i</m:mtext></m:msub></m:mrow></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math></equation><newline/> <equation id="fs-idp85327312" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mn>0.50</m:mn></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>7.7</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>0.50</m:mn></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0.15</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mn>15</m:mn><m:mi>%</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></equation><newline/> Þar sem einföldunarforsendan gildir ekki fyrir þetta kerfi er jafnvægisfastajafnan leyst á eftirfarandi hátt:<newline/> <equation id="fs-idm14221120" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>a</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1.2</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>0.50</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mrow></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math></equation><newline/> Með því að endurraða þessari jöfnu fæst<newline/> <equation id="fs-idm55224560" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>6.0</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>1.2</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msup><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mtext>2</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></equation><newline/> Ef jafnan er skrifuð á annars stigs formi fæst<newline/> <equation id="fs-idm46125840" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mtext>2</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>1.2</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>6.0</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></equation><newline/> Lausn fyrir rætur þessarar annars stigs jöfnu gefur neikvætt gildi sem má fleygja þar sem það er eðlisfræðilega ómarktækt og jákvætt gildi sem er jafnt <emphasis effect="italics">x</emphasis>. Eins og skilgreint er í ICE-töflunni er <emphasis effect="italics">x</emphasis> jafnt og styrkur hýdróníumjónarinnar.<newline/> <equation id="fs-idm217752528" class="unnumbered"><m:math>
<m:mtable columnalign="left">
<m:mtr>
<m:mtd>
<m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub>
<m:mtext>H</m:mtext>
<m:mn>3</m:mn>
</m:msub>
<m:msup>
<m:mtext>O</m:mtext>
<m:mo>+</m:mo>
</m:msup>
<m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0.072</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mi>M</m:mi>
</m:mtd>
</m:mtr>
<m:mtr>
<m:mtd>
<m:mtext>pH</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mtext>log</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub>
<m:mtext>H</m:mtext>
<m:mn>3</m:mn>
</m:msub>
<m:msup>
<m:mtext>O</m:mtext>
<m:mo>+</m:mo>
</m:msup>
<m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mtext>log</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mn>0.072</m:mn><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1.14</m:mn>
</m:mtd>
</m:mtr>
</m:mtable>
</m:math></equation></para>
<para id="fs-idm108532480"><title>Kannaðu þekkingu þína</title>Reiknaðu pH í 0,010-<emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> lausn af koffíni, veikum basa:</para>
<equation id="fs-idm108529312" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mtext>C</m:mtext><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mtext>N</m:mtext><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>l</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msub><m:mtext>C</m:mtext><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mtext>N</m:mtext><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="5em"/><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>b</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2.5</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−4</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<note id="fs-idm75099248">
<title>Answer:</title>
<para id="fs-idm30698512">pH 11,16</para>
</note>
</example>
</section>
<section id="fs-idm95688656">
<title>Áhrif sameindabyggingar á sýru-basa styrk</title>
<section id="fs-idm178147248">
<title>Tvífrumunga sýrur og basar</title>
<para id="fs-idm95688016">Þegar engin jöfnunaráhrif eru til staðar eykst sýrustyrkur tvífrumunga efnasambanda vetnis og málmleysingja (A) eftir því sem styrkur H-A efnatengisins minnkar niður eftir flokki í lotukerfinu. Fyrir flokk 17 er röðin eftir vaxandi sýrustigi HF &lt; HCl &lt; HBr &lt; HI. Sömuleiðis, fyrir flokk 16, er röðin eftir vaxandi sýrustyrk H<sub>2</sub>O &lt; H<sub>2</sub>S &lt; H<sub>2</sub>Se &lt; H<sub>2</sub>Te.</para>
<para id="fs-idp81297776">Þegar farið er þvert yfir lotu í lotukerfinu eykst sýrustyrkur tvíundar vetnissambanda með aukinni rafneikvæðni málmleysingjafrumeindarinnar vegna þess að skautun H-A tengisins eykst. Þannig er röðin fyrir vaxandi sýrustig (við brottnám einnar róteindar) þvert yfir aðra lotu CH<sub>4</sub> &lt; NH<sub>3</sub> &lt; H<sub>2</sub>O &lt; HF; þvert yfir þriðju lotu er hún SiH<sub>4</sub> &lt; PH<sub>3</sub> &lt; H<sub>2</sub>S &lt; HCl (sjá <link target-id="CNX_Chem_14_03_AcidpH"/>).</para>
<figure id="CNX_Chem_14_03_AcidpH" class="scaled-down">
<media id="fs-idp81301760" alt="This diagram has two rows and four columns. Red arrows point left across the bottom of the figure and down at the right side and are labeled “Increasing acid strength.” Blue arrows point left across the bottom and up at the right side of the figure and are labeled “Increasing base strength.” The first column is labeled 14 at the top and two white squares are beneath it. The first has the number 6 in the upper left corner and the formula C H subscript 4 in the center along with designation Neither acid nor base. The second square contains the number 14 in the upper left corner, the formula C H subscript 4 at the center and the designation Neither acid nor base. The second column is labeled 15 at the top and two blue squares are beneath it. The first has the number 7 in the upper left corner and the formula N H subscript 3 in the center along with the designation Weak base and K subscript b equals 1.8 times 10 superscript negative 5. The second square contains the number 15 in the upper left corner, the formula P H subscript 3 at the center and the designation Very weak base and K subscript b equals 4 times 10 superscript negative 28. The third column is labeled 16 at the top and two squares are beneath it. The first is shaded tan and has the number 8 in the upper left corner and the formula H subscript 2 O in the center along with the designation neutral. The second square is shaded pink, contains the number 16 in the upper left corner, the formula H subscript 2 S at the center and the designation Weak acid and K subscript a equals 9.5 times 10 superscript negative 8. The fourth column is labeled 17 at the top and two squares are beneath it. The first is shaded pink, has the number 9 in the upper left corner and the formula H F in the center along with the designation Weak acid and K subscript a equals 6.8 times 10 superscript negative 4. The second square is shaded a deeper pink, contains the number 17 in the upper left corner, the formula H C l at the center, and the designation Strong acid.">
<image mime-type="image/jpeg" src="../../media/CNX_Chem_14_03_AcidpH.jpg"/>
</media>
<caption>Myndin sýnir þróun í styrk tvíundarsýra og -basa.</caption>
</figure>
</section>
</section>
<section id="fs-idm222426752">
<title>Þríundarsýrur og -basar</title>
<para id="fs-idm107875680">Þríundarefnasambönd sem samanstanda af vetni, súrefni og einhverju þriðja frumefni („E“) geta haft byggingu eins og sýnt er á myndinni hér að neðan. Í þessum efnasamböndum er miðjufrumeindin E tengd einni eða fleiri O-frumeindum og að minnsta kosti ein af O-frumeindunum er einnig tengd H-frumeind, sem samsvarar almennu sameindaformúlunni O<sub>m</sub>E(OH)<sub>n</sub>. Þessi efnasambönd geta verið súr, basísk eða amfóterísk eftir eiginleikum miðjufrumeindarinnar E. Dæmi um slík efnasambönd eru brennisteinssýra, O<sub>2</sub>S(OH)<sub>2</sub>, brennisteinssýrlingur, OS(OH)<sub>2</sub>, saltpéturssýra, O<sub>2</sub>NOH, perklórsýra, O<sub>3</sub>ClOH, álhýdroxíð, Al(OH)<sub>3</sub>, kalsíumhýdroxíð, Ca(OH)<sub>2</sub>, og kalíumhýdroxíð, KOH:</para>
<media id="fs-idm107871568" class="scaled-down" alt="A diagram is shown that includes a central atom designated with the letter E. Single bonds extend above, below, left, and right of the E. An O atom is bonded to the right of the E, and an arrow points to the bond labeling it, “Bond a.” An H atom is single bonded to the right of the O atom. An arrow pointing to this bond connects it to the label, “Bond b.”">
<image mime-type="image/jpeg" src="../../media/CNX_Chem_14_03_OHbonds_img.jpg"/>
</media>
<para id="fs-idm107870208">Ef miðjufrumeindin, E, hefur lága rafneikvæðni er aðdráttarkraftur hennar á rafeindir lítill. Lítil tilhneiging er fyrir miðjufrumeindina til að mynda sterkt samgilt tengi við súrefnisfrumeindina og efnatengi <emphasis effect="italics">a</emphasis> milli frumefnisins og súrefnisins rofnar auðveldar en efnatengi <emphasis effect="italics">b</emphasis> milli súrefnis og vetnis. Þar af leiðandi er efnatengi <emphasis effect="italics">a</emphasis> jónískt, hýdroxíðjónir losna út í lausnina og efnið hegðar sér eins og basi — þetta á við um Ca(OH)<sub>2</sub> og KOH. Lægri rafneikvæðni er einkennandi fyrir málmkenndari frumefni; þess vegna mynda málmkennd frumefni jónísk hýdroxíð sem eru samkvæmt skilgreiningu basísk efnasambönd.</para>
<para id="fs-idm78964544">Ef frumeindin E hefur aftur á móti tiltölulega háa rafneikvæðni dregur hún sterklega að sér rafeindirnar sem hún deilir með súrefnisfrumeindinni, sem gerir efnatengi <emphasis effect="italics">a</emphasis> tiltölulega sterkt samgilt. Súrefnis-vetnis tengið, efnatengi <emphasis effect="italics">b</emphasis>, veikist þar með vegna þess að rafeindir færast í átt að E. Efnatengi <emphasis effect="italics">b</emphasis> er skautað og losar auðveldlega vetnisjónir út í lausnina, þannig að efnið hegðar sér eins og sýra. Há rafneikvæðni er einkennandi fyrir málmleysingja. Þannig mynda málmleysingjar samgild efnasambönd sem innihalda súra −OH hópa sem kallast <term id="term-00004">oxósýrur (e. oxyacids)</term>.</para>
<para id="fs-idm10523184">Að auka oxunartölu miðjufrumeindarinnar E eykur einnig sýrustig oxósýru vegna þess að það eykur aðdráttarkraft E á rafeindirnar sem hún deilir með súrefni og veikir þar með O-H tengið. Brennisteinssýra, H<sub>2</sub>SO<sub>4</sub>, eða O<sub>2</sub>S(OH)<sub>2</sub> (með oxunartölu brennisteins +6), er súrari en brennisteinssýrlingur, H<sub>2</sub>SO<sub>3</sub>, eða OS(OH)<sub>2</sub> (með oxunartölu brennisteins +4). Sömuleiðis er saltpéturssýra, HNO<sub>3</sub>, eða O<sub>2</sub>NOH (oxunartala N = +5), súrari en saltpéturssýrlingur, HNO<sub>2</sub>, eða ONOH (oxunartala N = +3). Í hvoru þessara para er oxunartala miðjufrumeindarinnar hærri fyrir sterkari sýruna (<link target-id="CNX_Chem_14_03_Oxyacid"/>).</para>
<figure id="CNX_Chem_14_03_Oxyacid" class="scaled-down">
<media id="fs-idm10517728" alt="A diagram is shown that includes four structural formulas for acids. A red, right pointing arrow is placed beneath the structures which is labeled “Increasing acid strength.” At the top left, the structure of Nitrous acid is provided. It includes an H atom to which an O atom with two unshared electron pairs is connected with a single bond to the right. A single bond extends to the right and slightly below to a N atom with one unshared electron pair. A double bond extends up and to the right from this N atom to an O atom which has two unshared electron pairs. To the upper right is a structure for Nitric acid. This structure differs from the previous structure in that the N atom is directly to the right of the first O atom and a second O atom with three unshared electron pairs is connected with a single bond below and to the right of the N atom which has no unshared electron pairs. At the lower left, an O atom with two unshared electron pairs is double bonded to its right to an S atom with a single unshared electron pair. An O atom with two unshared electron pairs is bonded above and an H atom is single bonded to this O atom. To the right of the S atom is a single bond to another O atom with two unshared electron pairs to which an H atom is single bonded. This structure is labeled “Sulfurous acid.” A similar structure which is labeled “Sulfuric acid” is placed in the lower right region of the figure. This structure differs in that an H atom is single bonded to the left of the first O atom, leaving it with two unshared electron pairs and a fourth O atom with two unshared electron pairs is double bonded beneath the S atom, leaving it with no unshared electron pairs.">
<image mime-type="image/jpeg" src="../../media/CNX_Chem_14_03_Oxyacid.jpg"/>
</media>
<caption>Þegar oxunartala miðjufrumeindarinnar E eykst, eykst sýrustigið einnig.</caption>
</figure>
<para id="fs-idm173312">Hýdroxíðsambönd frumefna með millistig rafneikvæðni og tiltölulega háar oxunartölur (til dæmis frumefni nálægt skálínunni sem skilur málma frá málmleysingjum í lotukerfinu) eru yfirleitt amfóterísk. Þetta þýðir að hýdroxíðsamböndin virka sem sýrur þegar þau hvarfast við sterka basa og sem basar þegar þau hvarfast við sterkar sýrur. Amfóterískir eiginleikar álhýdroxíðs, sem venjulega er til sem hýdratið Al(H<sub>2</sub>O)<sub>3</sub>(OH)<sub>3</sub>, endurspeglast í leysni þess í bæði sterkum sýrum og sterkum bösum. Í sterkum bösum breytist hið tiltölulega torleysta hýdrataða álhýdroxíð, Al(H<sub>2</sub>O)<sub>3</sub>(OH)<sub>3</sub>, í auðleystu jónina, <m:math><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mtext>Al</m:mtext><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>,</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> við efnahvarf við hýdroxíðjón:</para>
<equation id="fs-idm157855840" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>Al</m:mtext><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>l</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mtext>Al</m:mtext><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idp78683904">Í þessu efnahvarfi er róteind flutt frá einni af ál-tengdu H<sub>2</sub>O sameindunum yfir á hýdroxíðjón í lausninni. Efnasambandið Al(H<sub>2</sub>O)<sub>3</sub>(OH)<sub>3</sub> virkar því sem sýra við þessar aðstæður. Á hinn bóginn, þegar það er leyst upp í sterkum sýrum, breytist það í auðleystu jónina <m:math><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mtext>Al</m:mtext><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>3+</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> við efnahvarf við hýdróníumjón:</para>
<equation id="fs-idm10453568" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>3H</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mtext>Al</m:mtext><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mtext>Al</m:mtext><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mrow><m:mn>3+</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>3H</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>l</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idm223367024">Í þessu tilfelli eru róteindir fluttar frá hýdróníumjónum í lausninni yfir á Al(H<sub>2</sub>O)<sub>3</sub>(OH)<sub>3</sub>, og efnasambandið virkar sem basi.</para>
</section>
<section id="fs-idm223365360" class="summary">
<title>Lykilhugtök og samantekt</title>
<para id="fs-idm223364480">Hlutfallslegur styrkur sýra og basa endurspeglast í stærð jónunarfastanna þeirra; því sterkari sem sýran eða basinn er, því stærri er jónunarfasti hennar/hans. Gagnkvæmt samband er á milli styrks samoka sýru-basa pars: því sterkari sem sýran er, því veikari er samoka basi hennar. Vatn hefur jöfnunaráhrif á uppleystar sýrur eða basa og hvarfast að fullu til að mynda sín einkennandi hýdróníum- og hýdroxíðjónir (sterkasta sýran og basinn sem geta verið til í vatni). Styrkur tvíliða sýra eykst frá vinstri til hægri yfir lotu í lotukerfinu (CH<sub>4</sub> &lt; NH<sub>3</sub> &lt; H<sub>2</sub>O &lt; HF) og hann eykst niður eftir hóp (HF &lt; HCl &lt; HBr &lt; HI). Styrkur oxósýra sem innihalda sama miðjufrumefnið eykst eftir því sem oxunartala frumefnisins eykst (H<sub>2</sub>SO<sub>3</sub> &lt; H<sub>2</sub>SO<sub>4</sub>). Styrkur oxósýra eykst einnig eftir því sem rafneikvæðni miðjufrumefnisins eykst [H<sub>2</sub>SeO<sub>4</sub> &lt; H<sub>2</sub>SO<sub>4</sub>].</para>
</section>
<section id="fs-idp31338208" class="key-equations">
<title>Lykiljafna</title>
<table id="key-equations-table" class="unnumbered unstyled" summary="key equations table"><label/>
<tgroup cols="1"><colspec colnum="1" colname="c1"/>
<tbody>
<row><entry><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>a</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:msup><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mtext>A</m:mtext><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mo>]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mtext>HA</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mo>]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math></entry>
</row>
<row><entry><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>b</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>HB</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mo>]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>[</m:mo><m:mtext>B</m:mtext><m:mo>]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math></entry>
</row>
<row><entry><emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>a</sub> <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>b</sub> = 1,0 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−14</sup> = <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>w</sub></entry>
</row>
<row><entry><m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>Percent ionization</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:msup><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mtext>eq</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mtext>HA]</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:msub></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mn>100</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></entry>
</row>
</tbody></tgroup></table>
</section>
<section id="fs-idm94405216" class="exercises">
<title>Efnafræði – Verkefni í lok kafla</title>
<exercise id="fs-idm94404336">
<problem id="fs-idm94404080">
<para id="fs-idm94403824">Útskýrðu hvers vegna hlutleysingarhvarf sterkrar sýru og veiks basa gefur veikt súra lausn.</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idm94046624">
<problem id="fs-idm94046368">
<para id="fs-idm94046112">Útskýrðu hvers vegna hlutleysingarhvarf veikrar sýru og sterks basa gefur veikt basíska lausn.</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idm94045488">
<para id="fs-idm94045232">Saltið jónast í lausninni en anjónin hvarfast örlítið við vatn og myndar veiku sýruna. Þetta efnahvarf myndar einnig OH<sup>−</sup>, sem veldur því að lausnin verður basísk.</para>
</solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idm97090576">
<problem id="fs-idm97090320">
<para id="fs-idm97090064">Notaðu þennan lista yfir mikilvæg iðnaðarefnasambönd (og <link target-id="CNX_Chem_14_03_Corresp"/>) til að svara eftirfarandi spurningum varðandi: Ca(OH)<sub>2</sub>, CH<sub>3</sub>CO<sub>2</sub>H, HCl, H<sub>2</sub>CO<sub>3</sub>, HF, HNO<sub>2</sub>, HNO<sub>3</sub>, H<sub>3</sub>PO<sub>4</sub>, H<sub>2</sub>SO<sub>4</sub>, NH<sub>3</sub>, NaOH, Na<sub>2</sub>CO<sub>3</sub>.</para>
<para id="fs-idm5843184">(a) Tilgreindu sterkar Brønsted-Lowry sýrur og sterka Brønsted-Lowry basa.</para>
<para id="fs-idm5842624">(b) Tilgreindu þau efnasambönd sem geta hagað sér eins og Brønsted-Lowry sýrur með styrk á milli H<sub>3</sub>O<sup>+</sup> og H<sub>2</sub>O.</para>
<para id="fs-idm5839824">(c) Tilgreindu þau efnasambönd sem geta hagað sér eins og Brønsted-Lowry basar með styrk á milli H<sub>2</sub>O og OH<sup>−</sup>.</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idm102500528">
<problem id="fs-idm102500272">
<para id="fs-idm102500016">Edikslykt stafar af ediksýru, CH<sub>3</sub>CO<sub>2</sub>H, sem er veik sýra. Skráðu, í lækkandi röð eftir styrk, allar jóna- og sameindategundir sem eru til staðar í 1-<emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> vatnslausn af þessari sýru.</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idm157701984">
<para id="fs-idm157701728">[H<sub>2</sub>O] > [CH<sub>3</sub>CO<sub>2</sub>H] > <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:msup><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> ≈ <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> > [OH<sup>−</sup>]</para>
</solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idm81289984">
<problem id="fs-idm81289728">
<para id="fs-idm81289472">Heimilissalmiak er lausn af veika basanum NH<sub>3</sub> í vatni. Skráðu, í lækkandi röð eftir styrk, allar jóna- og sameindategundir sem eru til staðar í 1-<emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> vatnslausn af þessum basa.</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idm82919280">
<problem id="fs-idm82919024">
<para id="fs-idm82918768">Útskýrðu hvers vegna jónunarfastinn, <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>a</sub>, fyrir H<sub>2</sub>SO<sub>4</sub> er stærri en jónunarfastinn fyrir H<sub>2</sub>SO<sub>3</sub>.</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idm98075952">
<para id="fs-idm98075696">Oxunartala brennisteins í H<sub>2</sub>SO<sub>4</sub> er hærri en oxunartala brennisteins í H<sub>2</sub>SO<sub>3</sub>.</para>
</solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idm98073520">
<problem id="fs-idm98073264">
<para id="fs-idm98073008">Útskýrðu hvers vegna jónunarfastinn, <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>a</sub>, fyrir HI er stærri en jónunarfastinn fyrir HF.</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idm98070544">
<problem id="fs-idm98070288">
<para id="fs-idm98070032">Magasafi, meltingarvökvinn sem framleiddur er í maganum, inniheldur saltsýru, HCl. Magnesíummjólk, sem er grugga af föstu Mg(OH)<sub>2</sub> í vatnskenndum miðli, er stundum notuð til að hlutleysa umframmagns magasýru. Skrifaðu fulla, stillta jöfnu fyrir hlutleysingarhvarfið og tilgreindu samoka sýru-basa pörin.</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idp38933040">
<para id="fs-idp38933296"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mtable><m:mtr><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:mtext>Mg</m:mtext><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:mtext>2HCl</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo stretchy="false">⟶</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Mg</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>2+</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:msup><m:mtext>Cl</m:mtext><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>2H</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>l</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd></m:mtr><m:mtr><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:mtext>BB</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:mtext>BA</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd/><m:mtd/><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:mtext>CB</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:mtext>CA</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd/></m:mtr></m:mtable></m:mrow></m:math></para></solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp121913696">
<problem id="fs-idp10256960">
<para id="fs-idp10257216">Saltpéturssýra hvarfast við torleyst kopar(II)oxíð og myndar auðleyst kopar(II)nítrat, Cu(NO<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>, efnasamband sem hefur verið notað til að koma í veg fyrir þörungavöxt í sundlaugum. Skrifaðu stillta efnajöfnu fyrir efnahvarf vatnslausnar af HNO<sub>3</sub> við CuO.</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp54392720">
<problem id="fs-idp54392976">
<para id="fs-idp54393232">Hver er jónunarfastinn við 25 °C fyrir veiku sýruna <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>,</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math>, samoka sýru veika basans CH<sub>3</sub>NH<sub>2</sub>, <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>b</sub> = 4,4 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−4</sup>.</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idm79744112">
<para id="fs-idm79743856"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>a</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2.3</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−11</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></para>
</solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idm38113296">
<problem id="fs-idm38113040">
<para id="fs-idm38112784">Hver er jónunarfastinn við 25 °C fyrir veiku sýruna <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>,</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> samoka sýru veika basans (CH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>NH, <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>b</sub> = 5,9 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−4</sup>?</para></problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idm176650240">
<problem id="fs-idm176649984">
<para id="fs-idm176649728">Hvort er sterkari basinn, CH<sub>3</sub>NH<sub>2</sub> eða (CH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>NH? Hvor samoka sýran, <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> eða <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math>, er sterkari sýran?</para></problem>
<solution id="fs-idp68571296">
<para id="fs-idp68571552">Sterkari basinn eða sterkari sýran er sá/sú sem hefur hærra <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>b</sub> eða <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>a</sub> gildi. Í þessum tveimur dæmum eru það (CH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>NH og <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>.</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></para></solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp82803792">
<problem id="fs-idp82804048">
<para id="fs-idp82804304">Hvort er sterkari sýran, <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> eða HBrO?</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp38295632">
<problem id="fs-idp38295888">
<para id="fs-idp38296144">Hvort er sterkari basinn, (CH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>3</sub>N eða <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>BO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>?</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idp38299984">
<para id="fs-idp85603968">Tríetýlamín</para></solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idm157978560">
<problem id="fs-idm157978304">
<para id="fs-idm157978048">Spáðu fyrir um hvor sýran í eftirfarandi pörum er sterkari og útskýrðu rökstuðning þinn fyrir hvoru um sig.</para>
<para id="fs-idm157977552">(a) H<sub>2</sub>O eða HF</para>
<para id="fs-idm157976784">(b) B(OH)<sub>3</sub> eða Al(OH)<sub>3</sub></para>
<para id="fs-idm157975760">(c) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>HSO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> eða <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>HSO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<para id="fs-idm157971920">(d) NH<sub>3</sub> eða H<sub>2</sub>S</para>
<para id="fs-idp58796160">(e) H<sub>2</sub>O eða H<sub>2</sub>Te</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idm117245456">
<problem id="fs-idm117245200">
<para id="fs-idm117244944">Spáðu fyrir um hvort efnasambandið í hvoru eftirfarandi para af efnasamböndum er súrara og útskýrðu rökstuðning þinn fyrir hvoru um sig.</para>
<para id="fs-idm117244432">(a) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>HSO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> eða <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>HSeO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<para id="fs-idp39171888">(b) NH<sub>3</sub> eða H<sub>2</sub>O</para>
<para id="fs-idp39173040">(c) PH<sub>3</sub> eða HI</para>
<para id="fs-idp39173808">(d) NH<sub>3</sub> eða PH<sub>3</sub></para>
<para id="fs-idp39174832">(e) H<sub>2</sub>S eða HBr</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idp39175728">
<para id="fs-idp39175984">(a) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>HSO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>;</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> meiri rafneikvæðni miðjónarinnar. (b) H<sub>2</sub>O; NH<sub>3</sub> er basi og vatn er hlutlaust, eða ákvarðaðu á grundvelli <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>a</sub> gilda. (c) HI; PH<sub>3</sub> er veikara en HCl; HCl er veikara en HI. Því er PH<sub>3</sub> veikara en HI. (d) PH<sub>3</sub>; í tvíliða efnasamböndum vetnis og málmleysingja eykst sýrustigið fyrir frumefni neðar í hópnum. (e) HBr; í lotu eykst sýrustigið frá vinstri til hægri; í hóp eykst það ofan frá og niður. Br er til vinstri við og fyrir neðan S, þannig að HBr er sterkari sýran.</para>
</solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp33478144">
<problem id="fs-idp33478400">
<para id="fs-idp33478656">Raðaðu efnasamböndunum í hverjum eftirfarandi hópa eftir vaxandi sýrustigi eða basastigi, eins og gefið er til kynna, og útskýrðu röðina sem þú setur fram.</para>
<para id="fs-idp33479200">(a) sýrustig: HCl, HBr, HI</para>
<para id="fs-idp33479584">(b) basastig: H<sub>2</sub>O, OH<sup>−</sup>, H<sup>−</sup>, Cl<sup>−</sup></para>
<para id="fs-idp33481376">(c) basastig: Mg(OH)<sub>2</sub>, Si(OH)<sub>4</sub>, ClO<sub>3</sub>(OH) (Vísbending: Formúluna mætti einnig skrifa sem HClO<sub>4</sub>.)</para><para id="fs-idm14022912">(d) sýrustig: HF, H<sub>2</sub>O, NH<sub>3</sub>, CH<sub>4</sub></para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idm83972448">
<problem id="fs-idm83972192">
<para id="fs-idm83971936">Raðaðu efnasamböndunum í hverjum eftirfarandi hópa eftir vaxandi sýrustigi eða basastigi, eins og gefið er til kynna, og útskýrðu röðina sem þú setur fram.</para>
<para id="fs-idm83971392">(a) sýrustig: NaHSO<sub>3</sub>, NaHSeO<sub>3</sub>, NaHSO<sub>4</sub></para>
<para id="fs-idm83969984">(b) basastig: <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>BrO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>,</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>ClO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>,</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>IO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<para id="fs-idp33342400">(c) sýrustig: HOCl, HOBr, HOI</para>
<para id="fs-idp33342784">(d) sýrustig: HOCl, HOClO, HOClO<sub>2</sub>, HOClO<sub>3</sub></para>
<para id="fs-idp33343808">(e) basastig: <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>,</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> HS<sup>−</sup>, HTe<sup>−</sup>, <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>PH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<para id="fs-idp54362976">(f) basastig: BrO<sup>−</sup>, <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>BrO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>,</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>BrO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>,</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>BrO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idp54369632">
<para id="fs-idp10890112">(a) NaHSeO<sub>3</sub> &lt; NaHSO<sub>3</sub> &lt; NaHSO<sub>4</sub>; í fjöloxósýrum myndar rafneikvæðara miðjufrumefnið — í þessu tilfelli S — sterkari sýruna. Stærri fjöldi súrefnisfrumeinda á miðjufrumeindinni (sem gefur henni hærra oxunartal) veldur einnig meiri losun vetnisfrumeinda, sem leiðir til sterkari sýru. Sem salt eykst sýrustigið á sama hátt. (b) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>ClO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>&lt;</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>BrO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>&lt;</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>IO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>;</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> basastig anjónanna í röð sýra verður andstæðan við sýrustigið í oxósýrum þeirra. Sýrustigið eykst eftir því sem rafneikvæðni miðjufrumeindarinnar eykst. Cl er rafneikvæðara en Br og I er minnst rafneikvætt af þeim þremur. (c) HOI &lt; HOBr &lt; HOCl; í röð oxósýra af sömu gerð eykst sýrustigið eftir því sem rafneikvæðni miðjufrumeindarinnar eykst. Cl er rafneikvæðara en Br og I er minnst rafneikvætt af þeim þremur. (d) HOCl &lt; HOClO &lt; HOClO<sub>2</sub> &lt; HOClO<sub>3</sub>; í röð oxósýra með sama miðjufrumefni eykst sýrustigið eftir því sem fjöldi súrefnisfrumeinda eykst (eða eftir því sem oxunartal miðjufrumeindarinnar eykst). (e) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>HTe</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>&lt;</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>HS</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>&lt;&lt;</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>PH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>&lt;</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>;</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>PH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> og <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> eru anjónir veikra basa, þannig að þær virka sem sterkir basar gagnvart H<sup>+</sup>. <m:math><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mtext>HTe</m:mtext><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> og HS<sup>−</sup> eru anjónir veikra sýra, þannig að þær hafa minni basískan eiginleika. Í lotukerfishópi hefur rafneikvæðara frumefnið basískari anjón. (f) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>BrO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>&lt;</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>BrO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>&lt;</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>BrO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>&lt;</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>BrO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>;</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> með stærri fjölda súrefnisfrumeinda (þ.e. eftir því sem oxunartal miðjujónarinnar eykst) verður samsvarandi sýra súrari og anjónin þar af leiðandi minna basísk.</para>
</solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idm79428208">
<problem id="fs-idm79427952">
<para id="fs-idm79427696">Bæði HF og HCN jónast í vatni að takmörkuðu leyti. Hvor samsvarandi basinn, F<sup>−</sup> eða CN<sup>−</sup>, er sterkari basinn?</para></problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idm79424752">
<problem id="fs-idm79424496">
<para id="fs-idm79424240">Virka efnið sem myndast úr aspiríni í líkamanum er salisýlsýra, C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>4</sub>OH(CO<sub>2</sub>H). Karboxýlhópurinn (−CO<sub>2</sub>H) virkar sem veik sýra. Fenólhópurinn (OH-hópur tengdur arómatískum hring) virkar einnig sem sýra en mun veikari sýra. Skráðu, í röð eftir lækkandi styrk, allar jóna- og sameindategundir sem eru til staðar í 0,001-<emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> vatnslausn af C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>4</sub>OH(CO<sub>2</sub>H).</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idp9076048">
<para id="fs-idp9076304"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>></m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mtext>C</m:mtext><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>></m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>[H</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mtext>]</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mtext>0</m:mtext><m:mo>></m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>[C</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo>≫</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>C</m:mtext><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>></m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></para>
</solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idm81298048">
<problem id="fs-idm81297792">
<para id="fs-idm81297536">Eru styrkir oxóníumjónar og hýdroxíðjónar í lausn sýru eða basa í vatni í beinu eða öfugu hlutfalli? Útskýrðu svarið.</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp78760144">
<problem id="fs-idp78760400">
<para id="fs-idp78760656">Hvaða tvær algengu forsendur geta einfaldað útreikning á jafnvægisstyrkjum í lausn af veikri sýru eða basa?</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idp78761296">
<para id="fs-idp78761552">1. Gerðu ráð fyrir að hægt sé að vanrækja breytinguna á upphafsstyrk sýrunnar þegar jafnvægi er komið á, þannig að hægt sé að gera ráð fyrir að þessi styrkur sé fastur og jafn upphafsgildi heildarstyrks sýrunnar. 2. Gerðu ráð fyrir að við getum vanrækt framlag vatns til jafnvægisstyrks H<sub>3</sub>O<sup>+</sup>.</para>
</solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idm4769600">
<problem id="fs-idm4769344">
<para id="fs-idm4769088">Hvað af eftirfarandi mun auka hlutfall NH<sub>3</sub> sem breytist í ammóníumjón í vatni?</para>
<para id="fs-idm4768128">(a) álagning NaOH</para>
<para id="fs-idm4767744">(b) álagning HCl</para>
<para id="fs-idm4767360">(c) álagning NH<sub>4</sub>Cl</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idm4766464">
<para id="fs-idm4766208">(b) Álagning HCl</para>
</solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp75773712">
<problem id="fs-idp75773968">
<para id="fs-idp75774224">Hvað af eftirfarandi mun auka hlutfall HF sem breytist í flúoríðjón í vatni?</para>
<para id="fs-idp75774720">(a) álagning NaOH</para>
<para id="fs-idp75775104">(b) álagning HCl</para>
<para id="fs-idp75775488">(c) álagning NaF</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp5155408">
<problem id="fs-idp5155664">
<para id="fs-idp5155920">Hver eru áhrifin á styrk <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>,</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> HNO<sub>2</sub> og OH<sup>−</sup> þegar eftirfarandi er bætt við lausn af KNO<sub>2</sub> í vatni:</para>
<para id="fs-idp5159504">(a) HCl</para>
<para id="fs-idp5159888">(b) HNO<sub>2</sub></para>
<para id="fs-idp5160528">(c) NaOH</para>
<para id="fs-idp5160912">(d) NaCl</para>
<para id="fs-idp38077152">(e) KNO<sub>2</sub></para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idm87543168">
<para id="fs-idm87542912">(a) Með því að bæta við HCl bætast við H<sub>3</sub>O<sup>+</sup> jónir, sem hvarfast þá við OH<sup>−</sup> jónirnar og lækka styrk þeirra. Jafnvægið hliðrast til hægri, sem eykur styrk HNO<sub>2</sub> og minnkar styrk <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> jóna. (b) Með því að bæta við HNO<sub>2</sub> eykst styrkur HNO<sub>2</sub> og jafnvægið hliðrast til vinstri, sem eykur styrk <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> jóna og minnkar styrk OH<sup>−</sup> jóna. (c) Með því að bæta við NaOH bætast við OH<sup>−</sup> jónir, sem hliðrar jafnvæginu til vinstri, eykur styrk <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> jóna og minnkar styrk HNO<sub>2</sub>. (d) Álagning NaCl hefur engin áhrif á styrk jónanna. (e) Með því að bæta við KNO<sub>2</sub> bætast við <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> jónir og jafnvægið hliðrast til hægri, sem eykur styrk HNO<sub>2</sub> og OH<sup>−</sup> jóna.</para>
</solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp58815696">
<problem id="fs-idp58815952">
<para id="fs-idp58816208">Hver eru áhrifin á styrk flúorsýru, hýdróníumjónar og flúoríðjónar þegar eftirfarandi efnum er bætt við aðskildar lausnir af flúorsýru?</para>
<para id="fs-idp58816768">(a) HCl</para>
<para id="fs-idp58817152">(b) KF</para>
<para id="fs-idp58817536">(c) NaCl</para>
<para id="fs-idp58817920">(d) KOH</para>
<para id="fs-idp58818304">(e) HF</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idm13803280">
<problem id="fs-idm13803024">
<para id="fs-idm13802768">Af hverju ræðst styrkur hýdróníumjóna í lausn sem er 0,10 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> í HCl og 0,10 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> í HCOOH af styrk HCl?</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idm13801008">
<para id="fs-idm13800752">Þetta er tilfelli þar sem lausnin inniheldur efnablöndu af sýrum með mismunandi jónunarstyrk. Í lausninni er HCO<sub>2</sub>H aðallega til staðar sem HCO<sub>2</sub>H sameindir vegna þess að jónun veiku sýrunnar er bæld niður af sterku sýrunni. Þess vegna leggur HCO<sub>2</sub>H óverulegt magn af hýdróníumjónum til lausnarinnar. Sterkari sýran, HCl, er ríkjandi framleiðandi hýdróníumjóna vegna þess að hún er fullkomlega jónuð. Í slíkri lausn ákvarðar sterkari sýran styrk hýdróníumjóna og jónun veikari sýrunnar er ákvörðuð af [H<sub>3</sub>O<sup>+</sup>] sem sterkari sýran framleiðir.</para>
</solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idm65088304">
<problem id="fs-idm65088048">
<para id="fs-idm65087792">Út frá gefnum jafnvægisstyrkjum, reiknaðu <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>a</sub> fyrir hverja af veiku sýrunum og <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>b</sub> fyrir hvern af veiku bösunum.</para>
<para id="fs-idm109267584">(a) CH<sub>3</sub>CO<sub>2</sub>H: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:msup><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> = 1,34 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−3</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>;<newline/> <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> = 1,34 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−3</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>;</para>
<para id="fs-idm113309072">[CH<sub>3</sub>CO<sub>2</sub>H] = 9,866 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−2</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>;</para>
<para id="fs-idm113306400">(b) ClO<sup>−</sup>: [OH<sup>−</sup>] = 4,0 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−4</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>;</para>
<para id="fs-idp36189824">[HClO] = 2,38 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−4</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>;</para>
<para id="fs-idp36191728">[ClO<sup>−</sup>] = 0,273 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>;</para>
<para id="fs-idp36193120">(c) HCO<sub>2</sub>H: [HCO<sub>2</sub>H] = 0,524 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>;<newline/> <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:msup><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> = 9,8 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−3</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>;<newline/> <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>HCO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> = 9,8 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−3</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>;</para>
<para id="fs-idm83737680">(d) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mtext>C</m:mtext><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>:</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>C</m:mtext><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> = 0,233 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>;</para>
<para id="fs-idm121296080">[C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>5</sub>NH<sub>2</sub>] = 2,3 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−3</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>;<newline/> <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:msup><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> = 2,3 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−3</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis></para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp68108464">
<problem id="fs-idp68108720">
<para id="fs-idp68108976">Út frá gefnum jafnvægisstyrkjum, reiknaðu <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>a</sub> fyrir hverja af veiku sýrunum og <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>b</sub> fyrir hvern af veiku bösunum.</para>
<para id="fs-idp68111120">(a) NH<sub>3</sub>: [OH<sup>−</sup>] = 3,1 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−3</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>;<newline/> <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> = 3,1 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−3</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>;</para>
<para id="fs-idp69240176">[NH<sub>3</sub>] = 0,533 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>;</para>
<para id="fs-idp69241568">(b) HNO<sub>2</sub>: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:msup><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> = 0,011 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>;<newline/> <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> = 0,0438 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>;</para>
<para id="fs-idm1577296">[HNO<sub>2</sub>] = 1,07 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>;</para>
<para id="fs-idm1575904">(c) (CH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>3</sub>N: [(CH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>3</sub>N] = 0,25 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>;<newline/> [(CH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>3</sub>NH<sup>+</sup>] = 4,3 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−3</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>;</para>
<para id="fs-idm94284096">[OH<sup>−</sup>] = 3,7 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−3</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>;</para>
<para id="fs-idm94281808">(d) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>:</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> = 0,100 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>;</para>
<para id="fs-idp54458608">[NH<sub>3</sub>] = 7,5 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−6</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>;<newline/> [H<sub>3</sub>O<sup>+</sup>] = 7,5 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−6</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis></para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idm78118384">
<para id="fs-idm78118128">(a) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>b</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1.8</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−5</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo>;</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> (b) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>a</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4.5</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−4</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo>;</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> (c) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>b</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>6.4</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−5</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo>;</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> (d) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>a</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>5.6</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−10</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></para></solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp58811168">
<problem id="fs-idp58811424">
<para id="fs-idp58811680">Ákvarðaðu <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>b</sub> fyrir nítrítjónina, <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>.</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> Í 0,10-<emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> lausn er þessi basi 0,0015% jónaður.</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idm71105088">
<problem id="fs-idm71104832">
<para id="fs-idm71104576">Ákvarðaðu <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>a</sub> fyrir vetnissúlfatjónina, <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>HSO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>.</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> Í 0,10-<emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> lausn er sýran 29% jónuð.</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idm71100512">
<para id="fs-idm71100256"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>a</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1.2</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></para>
</solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idm5851168">
<problem id="fs-idm5850912">
<para id="fs-idm5850656">Reiknaðu jónunarfastann fyrir hverja af eftirfarandi sýrum eða bösum út frá jónunarfasta samoka basa þeirra eða samoka sýru:</para>
<para id="fs-idm5850112">(a) F<sup>−</sup></para>
<para id="fs-idm5849472">(b) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<para id="fs-idp69550272">(c) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>AsO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mrow><m:mn>3−</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<para id="fs-idp69552448">(d) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<para id="fs-idp69556896">(e) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<para id="fs-idp69558944">(f) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>HC</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> (sem basi)</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idm82380304">
<problem id="fs-idm82380048">
<para id="fs-idm82379792">Reiknaðu jónunarfastann fyrir hverja af eftirfarandi sýrum eða bösum út frá jónunarfasta samoka basa þeirra eða samoka sýru:</para>
<para id="fs-idm82379248">(a) HTe<sup>−</sup> (sem basi)</para>
<para id="fs-idm82378480">(b) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>NH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<para id="fs-idm82374672">(c) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>HAsO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mrow><m:mn>2–</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> (sem basi)</para>
<para id="fs-idm82372368">(d) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>HO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> (sem basi)</para>
<para id="fs-idm82370192">(e) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mtext>C</m:mtext><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<para id="fs-idp30723328">(f) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>HSO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> (sem basi)</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idp30725632">
<para id="fs-idp30725888">(a) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>b</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4.3</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−12</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> (b) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>a</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1.6</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> (c) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>b</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>5.9</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> (d) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>b</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4.2</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> (e) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>b</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2.3</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> (f) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>b</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>6.3</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−13</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></para></solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idm8587472">
<problem id="fs-idm8587216">
<para id="fs-idm8586960">Notaðu <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>a</sub> gildið 1,4 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−5</sup> til að staðsetja <m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>Al</m:mtext><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mrow><m:mn>3+</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> á réttum stað í <link target-id="CNX_Chem_14_03_strengths"/>.</para></problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp3008704">
<problem id="fs-idp3008960">
<para id="fs-idp3009216">Reiknaðu styrk allra tegunda leystra efna í hverri af eftirfarandi lausnum af sýrum eða bösum. Gerðu ráð fyrir að hægt sé að vanrækja jónun vatns og sýndu fram á að hægt sé að vanrækja breytinguna á upphafsstyrknum.</para>
<para id="fs-idp3011616">(a) 0,0092 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> HClO, veik sýra</para>
<para id="fs-idp3012624">(b) 0,0784 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>5</sub>NH<sub>2</sub>, veikur basi</para>
<para id="fs-idp3014784">(c) 0,0810 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> HCN, veik sýra</para>
<para id="fs-idp3015792">(d) 0,11 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> (CH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>3</sub>N, veikur basi</para>
<para id="fs-idp3017568">(e) 0,120 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> <m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>Fe</m:mtext><m:msub><m:mrow>
<m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/>
<m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mrow><m:mn>2+</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> veik sýra, <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>a</sub> = 1,6 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−7</sup></para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idm97049136">
<para id="fs-idm97048880">(a) <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:msup><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo>
<m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>ClO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mtext>HClO</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/>
<m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mn>0.0092</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mfrac>
<m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>≈</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>0.0092</m:mn></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2.9</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−8</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> <newline/> Lausn fyrir <emphasis effect="italics">x</emphasis> gefur 1,63 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−5</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>. Þetta gildi er minna en 5% af 0,0092, þannig að forsendan um að hægt sé að vanrækja það er gild. Því er styrkur leystra efna við jafnvægi:<newline/> [H<sub>3</sub>O<sup>+</sup>] = [ClO<sup>–</sup>] = 1,6 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−5</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis><newline/> [HClO<sup>–</sup>] = 0,0092 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis><newline/> [OH<sup>−</sup>] = 6,1 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−10</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>;<newline/> (b) <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>C</m:mtext><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/>
<m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/>
<m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>C</m:mtext><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mn>0.0784</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>≈</m:mo>
<m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>0.0784</m:mn></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4.3</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−10</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> <newline/> Lausn fyrir <emphasis effect="italics">x</emphasis> gefur 5,81 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−6</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>. Þetta gildi er minna en 5% af 0,0784, þannig að forsendan um að hægt sé að vanrækja það er gild. Því er styrkur leystra efna við jafnvægi:<newline/> <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>C</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>H</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>5</m:mn>
<m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> = [OH<sup>−</sup>] = 5,8 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−6</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> <newline/> [C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>5</sub>NH<sub>2</sub>] = 0,0784 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis><newline/> [H<sub>3</sub>O<sup>+</sup>] = 1,7<m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−9</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>;<newline/> (c) <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:msup><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>CN</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mtext>HCN</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mn>0.0810</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>≈</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>0.0810</m:mn></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4.9</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−10</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math><newline/> Lausn fyrir <emphasis effect="italics">x</emphasis> gefur 6,30 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−6</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>. Þetta gildi er minna en 5% af 0,0810, þannig að forsendan um að hægt sé að vanrækja það er gild. Því er styrkur leystra efna við jafnvægi:<newline/> [H<sub>3</sub>O<sup>+</sup>] = [CN<sup>−</sup>] = 6,3 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−6</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis><newline/> [HCN] = 0,0810 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis><newline/> [OH<sup>−</sup>] = 1,6 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−9</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>;<newline/> (d) <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>NH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>N</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mn>0.11</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>≈</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>0.11</m:mn></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>6.3</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−5</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math><newline/> Lausn fyrir <emphasis effect="italics">x</emphasis> gefur 2,63 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−3</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>. Þetta gildi er minna en 5% af 0,11, þannig að forsendan um að hægt sé að vanrækja það er gild. Því er styrkur leystra efna við jafnvægi:<newline/> [(CH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>3</sub>NH<sup>+</sup>] = [OH<sup>−</sup>] = 2,6 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−3</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis><newline/> [(CH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>3</sub>N] = 0,11 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis><newline/> [H<sub>3</sub>O<sup>+</sup>] = 3,8 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−12</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>;<newline/> (e) <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mtext>Fe</m:mtext><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:msup><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mtext>Fe</m:mtext><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mrow><m:mn>2+</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mn>0.120</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>≈</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>0.120</m:mn></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1.6</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−7</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math><newline/> Lausn fyrir <emphasis effect="italics">x</emphasis> gefur 1,39 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−4</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>. Þetta gildi er minna en 5% af 0,120, þannig að forsendan um að hægt sé að vanrækja það er gild. Því er styrkur leystra efna við jafnvægi:<newline/> [Fe(H<sub>2</sub>O)<sub>5</sub>(OH)<sup>+</sup>] = [H<sub>3</sub>O<sup>+</sup>] = 1,4 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−4</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis><newline/> <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mtext>Fe</m:mtext><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mrow><m:mn>2+</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> = 0,120 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis><newline/> [OH<sup>−</sup>] = 7,2 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−11</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis></para></solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idm78141920">
<problem id="fs-idm78141664">
<para id="fs-idm78141408">Própíónsýra, C<sub>2</sub>H<sub>5</sub>CO<sub>2</sub>H (<emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>a</sub> = 1,34 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−5</sup>), er notuð við framleiðslu á kalsíumprópíónati, sem er rotvarnarefni í matvælum. Hvert er pH 0,698-<emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> lausnar af C<sub>2</sub>H<sub>5</sub>CO<sub>2</sub>H?</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp35201920">
<problem id="fs-idp35202176">
<para id="fs-idp35202432">Hvítt edik er 5,0% massalausn af ediksýru í vatni. Ef eðlismassi hvíts ediks er 1,007 g/cm<sup>3</sup>, hvert er pH-gildið?</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idp35203456">
<para id="fs-idp35203712">pH = 2,41</para>
</solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idm68637072">
<problem id="fs-idm68636816">
<para id="fs-idm68636560">Jónunarfasti mjólkursýru, CH<sub>3</sub>CH(OH)CO<sub>2</sub>H, sýru sem finnst í blóði eftir mikla áreynslu, er 1,36 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−4</sup>. Ef 20,0 g af mjólkursýru eru notuð til að búa til lausn með rúmmálið 1,00 L, hver er þá styrkur hýdróníumjónarinnar í lausninni?</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idm75310368">
<problem id="fs-idm75310112">
<para id="fs-idm75309856">Nikótín, C<sub>10</sub>H<sub>14</sub>N<sub>2</sub>, er basi sem getur tekið við tveimur róteindum (<emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>b1</sub> = 7 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−7</sup>, <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>b2</sub> = 1,4 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−11</sup>). Hver er styrkur hverrar efnisagnar sem er til staðar í 0,050-<emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> lausn af nikótíni?</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idm83649184">
<para id="fs-idm83648928">[C<sub>10</sub>H<sub>14</sub>N<sub>2</sub>] = 0,049 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>; [C<sub>10</sub>H<sub>14</sub>N<sub>2</sub>H<sup>+</sup>] = 1,9 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−4</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>; <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>C</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>14</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mtext>N</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mrow><m:mn>2+</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> = 1,4 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−11</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>; [OH<sup>−</sup>] = 1,9 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−4</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>; [H<sub>3</sub>O<sup>+</sup>] = 5,3 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−11</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis></para></solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp85725440">
<problem id="fs-idp85725696">
<para id="fs-idp85725952">pH-gildi 0,23-<emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> lausnar af HF er 1,92. Ákvarðaðu <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>a</sub> fyrir HF út frá þessum gögnum.</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idm95676256">
<problem id="fs-idm95676000">
<para id="fs-idm95675744">pH-gildi 0,15-<emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> lausnar af <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>HSO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> er 1,43. Ákvarðaðu <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>a</sub> fyrir <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>HSO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> út frá þessum gögnum.</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idm95670144">
<para id="fs-idm95669888"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>a</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1.2</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></para>
</solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idm82940432">
<problem id="fs-idm82940176">
<para id="fs-idm82939920">pH-gildi 0,10-<emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> lausnar af koffíni er 11,70. Ákvarðaðu <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>b</sub> fyrir koffín út frá þessum gögnum:<newline/> <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mtext>C</m:mtext><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mtext>N</m:mtext><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>l</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msub><m:mtext>C</m:mtext><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mtext>N</m:mtext><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mrow/><m:msup><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idm93044768">
<problem id="fs-idm93044512">
<para id="fs-idm93044256">pH-gildi lausnar af heimilisammoníaki, 0,950 M lausn af NH<sub>3,</sub> er 11,612. Ákvarðaðu <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>b</sub> fyrir NH<sub>3</sub> út frá þessum gögnum.</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idm93042096">
<para id="fs-idm93041840"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>b</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1.77</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−5</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></para>
</solution>
</exercise>
</section>
</content>
<glossary>
<definition id="fs-idp86058640">
<term>sýrujónun<sub>a</sub>rfasti (<emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis>a) (e. acid ionization constant (ka))</term>
<meaning id="fs-idp86058640-meaning">jafnvægisfasti fyrir sýrujónunarhvarf</meaning>
</definition>
<definition id="fs-idp86060672">
<term><sub>b</sub>asajónunarfasti (<emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis>b) (e. base ionization constant (kb))</term>
<meaning id="fs-idp86060672-meaning">jafnvægisfasti fyrir basajónunarhvarf</meaning>
</definition>
<definition id="fs-idm94080720">
<term>jöfnunaráhrif (e. leveling effect)</term>
<meaning id="fs-idm94080720-meaning">sú athugun að sýru-basastyrkur uppleystra efna í tilteknum leysi takmarkast við styrk einkennandi sýru- og basaefnisagna leysisins (í vatni, hýdróníum- og hýdroxíðjónir, í sömu röð)</meaning>
</definition>
<definition id="fs-idm94074528">
<term>oxósýra (e. oxyacid)</term>
<meaning id="fs-idm94074528-meaning">þrískipt efnasamband með súra eiginleika, en sameindir þess innihalda miðlæga málmleysingjafrumeind sem er tengd einni eða fleiri O-frumeindum, þar sem að minnsta kosti ein þeirra er tengd jónanlegri H-frumeind</meaning>
</definition>
<definition id="fs-idm94073376">
<term>jónunarprósenta (e. percent ionization)</term>
<meaning id="fs-idm94073376-meaning">hlutfall styrks jónaðrar sýru og upphafsstyrks sýru, gefið upp sem prósentutala</meaning>
</definition>
</glossary>
</document>